<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA41">
<l>kuṉṟaṉaiya kuṟṟañ ceyiṉuṅ kuṇaṅkoḷḷu</l>
<l>miṉṟumuta lāka veṉṉeñcē – yeṉṟum</l>
<l>puṟaṉuraiyē yāyiṉum poṉṉāḻik kaiyāṉ</l>
<l>ṟiṟaṉuraiyē cintit tiru</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>From today onwards, o my heart,</l>
<l>that takes it for merit, even if it commits a fault as [big] as a mountain,</l>
<l>always keep thinking of words on the matter</l>
<l>of him in whose hand is the golden discus, even if it is but slanderous words.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
